WEBVTT

00:48.173 --> 00:53.595
 <i>[Faraday] This is</i>
 <i>my human voice.</i>

00:56.514 --> 00:57.932
 <i>Hello.</i>

00:57.974 --> 01:01.561
 <i>I hope this signal</i>
 <i>reaches you on Anthea.</i>

01:02.604 --> 01:04.439
 <i>I "hope."</i>

01:05.231 --> 01:08.276
 <i>That's a word</i>
 <i>you don't understand.</i>

01:12.864 --> 01:17.077
<i>On Earth,</i>
<i>you would be called</i>

01:17.077 --> 01:18.912
<i>my wife.</i>

01:28.129 --> 01:31.841
<i>Our offspring would be known</i>

01:31.841 --> 01:34.552
<i>as our children.</i>

01:44.562 --> 01:49.776
<i>When I left you,</i>
<i>I felt no doubt or regret.</i>

01:52.195 --> 01:55.115
<i>There was only the task ahead.</i>

01:59.327 --> 02:04.124
<i>But now something impossible</i>
<i>is happening to me.</i>

02:04.666 --> 02:06.000
<i>Emotion.</i>

02:06.543 --> 02:08.378
 <i>Human emotion.</i>

02:08.378 --> 02:11.923
 <i>It has no application</i>
 <i>in Anthean.</i>

02:11.923 --> 02:14.050
 <i>My adept, Thomas Newton,</i>

02:14.050 --> 02:16.469
 <i>used these television signals</i>
 <i>to communicate with his wife</i>

02:16.511 --> 02:19.806
 <i>as I am now</i>
 <i>communicating with you.</i>

02:20.557 --> 02:23.434
 <i>I'm sending this message</i>
 <i>to try and explain</i>

02:23.476 --> 02:25.603
 <i>what's happening to me.</i>

02:25.603 --> 02:29.149
 <i>I seem to be</i>
 <i>going through some ch...</i>

02:31.609 --> 02:33.695
 <i>Changes.</i>

02:45.540 --> 02:50.295
<i>I translated Newton's design</i>
<i>for a quantum fusion machine,</i>

02:50.336 --> 02:52.172
<i>but that was</i>
<i>only the beginning.</i>

02:52.172 --> 02:55.091
 <i>There were still</i>
 <i>two phases left to complete.</i>

02:55.133 --> 02:57.302
 <i>Phase one, build it.</i>

02:57.302 --> 02:59.512
 <i>[whirring]</i>

02:59.512 --> 03:03.558
<i>Phase two, identify</i>
<i>a fuel model to power it.</i>

03:03.558 --> 03:07.020
<i>This is where</i>
<i>things began to unravel.</i>

03:07.061 --> 03:08.021
 <i>Mm-mmm. No.</i>

03:08.021 --> 03:11.566
 <i>Hydrogen-protium,</i>
 <i>deuterium, tritium...</i>

03:11.608 --> 03:14.694
 <i>All known power sources</i>
 <i>for achieving fusion</i>

03:14.736 --> 03:17.697
 <i>simply did not apply</i>
 <i>to Newton's design.</i>

03:17.739 --> 03:22.202
<i>This meant we had the machine,</i>
<i>but no way to activate it.</i>

03:22.202 --> 03:25.163
 <i>[engine roaring]</i>

03:27.498 --> 03:31.169
<i>Why would Newton summon me</i>
<i>light-years across the galaxy</i>

03:31.169 --> 03:33.338
<i>to follow instructions</i>
<i>that were impossible?</i>

03:33.379 --> 03:37.550
 <i>When the survival of two planets</i>
 <i>depends on my success?</i>

03:37.926 --> 03:40.011
 <i>It made no sense.</i>

03:40.053 --> 03:42.096
 <i>And then I remembered</i>
 <i>what he said.</i>

03:42.096 --> 03:46.893
 <i>Humans... You have to</i>
 <i>see with their eyes.</i>

03:48.311 --> 03:51.773
 <i>I didn't know what he meant,</i>
 <i>or why he said it.</i>

03:51.814 --> 03:53.358
 <i>But I had to try.</i>

03:53.358 --> 03:57.737
 <i>So I initiated a study</i>
 <i>of what makes humans...</i>

03:59.697 --> 04:00.907
 <i>human.</i>

04:04.911 --> 04:08.873
<i>A controlled experiment</i>
<i>requires a vantage point.</i>

04:08.873 --> 04:13.461
<i>I chose the 21st-century</i>
<i>incarnation of the water hole.</i>

04:14.837 --> 04:16.881
 <i>[indistinct chatter]</i>

04:20.385 --> 04:25.098
<i>On Anthea, as drones,</i>
<i>we exist without choice.</i>

04:25.139 --> 04:27.934
<i>There are no decisions</i>
<i>or alternatives.</i>

04:27.976 --> 04:29.894
<i>No variety or preference.</i>

04:29.936 --> 04:34.357
<i>There are only assigned tasks</i>
<i>and their completion.</i>

04:34.399 --> 04:36.192
<i>But here on Earth,</i>

04:36.192 --> 04:41.364
 <i>the amount of choices humans</i>
 <i>allow themselves is dizzying.</i>

04:41.364 --> 04:44.617
<i>Macchiato, double latte,</i>
<i>salted caramel,</i>

04:44.617 --> 04:46.953
<i>mocha melon chip,</i>
<i>Vienna espresso,</i>

04:46.995 --> 04:48.496
<i>apple crisp, cafe au lait,</i>

04:48.496 --> 04:51.416
<i>Affogato, pumpkin spice</i>
<i>no whip, half Capp,</i>

04:51.457 --> 04:52.709
<i>pumpkin whip Americano,</i>

04:52.750 --> 04:55.628
 <i>Rwanda Hingakawa</i>
 <i>macchiato, Gala black,</i>

04:55.628 --> 04:57.213
 <i>double reserve, dip, drip,</i>

04:57.255 --> 04:59.340
 <i>no foam, no whip,</i>
 <i>fat-free drizzle.</i>

04:59.340 --> 05:00.633
 <i>[doorbell rings]</i>

05:01.926 --> 05:03.678
 <i>Mom says</i>
 <i>if you don't like turnip,</i>

05:03.678 --> 05:06.222
 <i>then I have to eat</i>
 <i>the turnip you don't eat,</i>

05:06.222 --> 05:08.099
 <i>so please like turnip.</i>

05:08.099 --> 05:12.312
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Here,</i>
<i>a pupa is called a child.</i>

05:13.021 --> 05:15.106
 <i>And even they have choices.</i>

05:15.148 --> 05:16.899
 <i>Our children</i>
 <i>were taught to obey,</i>

05:16.899 --> 05:21.154
<i>but these children are</i>
<i>tiny instruments of chaos.</i>

05:22.030 --> 05:24.157
 <i>Humans also make</i>
 <i>elaborate rituals</i>

05:24.157 --> 05:26.034
 <i>of their most basic functions.</i>

05:26.034 --> 05:28.828
 <i>All unnecessarily complex.</i>

05:28.828 --> 05:30.538
 <i>Case in point...</i>

05:30.580 --> 05:32.415
<i>The family consumption ritual.</i>

05:32.457 --> 05:42.050
<i>La-la la-la la la la la</i>
<i>La-la la-la la la la la</i>

05:42.050 --> 05:44.761
<i>La la la la la la </i>

05:44.761 --> 05:47.680
 <i>How is this a benefit</i>
 <i>to anything?</i>

05:48.973 --> 05:51.976
 <i>Stove, table, plate.</i>

05:52.435 --> 05:53.686
 <i>So many stations.</i>

05:53.686 --> 05:57.148
 <i>They're opportunities for things</i>
 <i>to fall off your plate.</i>

05:57.148 --> 05:58.358
 <i>[whispers] Like turnips.</i>

05:58.358 --> 06:00.651
 <i>You want to off-gas the turnips?</i>

06:00.651 --> 06:03.029
 <i>[laughs] You said gas.</i>

06:03.029 --> 06:03.905
 <i>Larva gas.</i>

06:03.905 --> 06:06.324
 <i>Should we hover over</i>
 <i>a bucket on the floor?</i>

06:06.324 --> 06:08.451
 <i>That's not how</i>
 <i>we do it on Anthea.</i>

06:08.451 --> 06:10.787
 <i>-Where's Anthea?</i>
 <i>-[both] Canada.</i>

06:10.787 --> 06:11.996
 <i>[Josiah] Mm-hmm.</i>

06:12.038 --> 06:14.165
 <i>And then, this happens.</i>

06:15.500 --> 06:17.627
 <i>They speak to their God.</i>

06:17.627 --> 06:19.253
 <i>Thank you, Lord,</i>
 <i>for the food</i>

06:19.295 --> 06:20.755
 <i>we're about to receive</i>
 <i>to nourish our bodies</i>

06:20.797 --> 06:23.216
 <i>and keep us mindful</i>
 <i>of the needs of others.</i>

06:24.258 --> 06:26.719
 <i>Almighty God, thank you. Amen.</i>

06:27.261 --> 06:28.513
 <i>Complicated.</i>

06:28.554 --> 06:30.390
 <i>I'll return to this.</i>

06:30.390 --> 06:32.350
 <i>What did you do today,</i>
 <i>Molly Molls?</i>

06:32.350 --> 06:34.394
 <i>You only made</i>
 <i>a stairway to heaven</i>

06:34.394 --> 06:37.522
 <i>out of all the blue Lego,</i>
 <i>Miss Ingrate.</i>

06:37.522 --> 06:39.399
 <i>How was your day today</i>
 <i>at the lab?</i>

06:39.440 --> 06:42.693
 <i>-He made a first impression.</i>
 <i>-I made a first impression.</i>

06:42.735 --> 06:44.153
 <i>You should've seen Juzzie's</i>

06:44.153 --> 06:46.197
 <i>first day as the boss</i>
 <i>of her lab.</i>

06:46.239 --> 06:47.990
 <i>She literally forgot words.</i>

06:48.032 --> 06:50.660
 <i>People don't forget words,</i>
 <i>people have brain farts.</i>

06:50.660 --> 06:53.579
 <i>[chuckling] What's with</i>
 <i>the gas and farts today?</i>

06:53.621 --> 06:55.623
 <i>[whispers] I just made one.</i>

06:55.623 --> 06:58.000
 <i>[all laughing]</i>

06:58.042 --> 06:59.961
 <i>Here you go,</i>
 <i>Miss Farty Pants.</i>

06:59.961 --> 07:01.295
 <i>[all laughing]</i>

07:01.295 --> 07:03.756
 <i>Something else they have here...</i>

07:04.215 --> 07:06.801
 <i>They call it "joy."</i>

07:07.552 --> 07:08.803
 <i>An emotion that exists</i>

07:08.803 --> 07:12.932
 <i>on the far positive end</i>
 <i>of their spectrum.</i>

07:19.856 --> 07:24.861
<i>Disruptive as it is, it appears</i>
<i>to be the ultimate objective.</i>

07:24.902 --> 07:28.072
<i>As commonly occurring</i>
<i>and taken for granted</i>

07:28.114 --> 07:32.785
<i>as it is rare and elusive.</i>

07:33.619 --> 07:37.790
 <i>Wife, there was</i>
 <i>a moment I wished...</i>

07:39.417 --> 07:41.586
 <i>That's another word</i>
 <i>they have here.</i>

07:41.627 --> 07:44.422
 <i>I wished for you</i>
 <i>to have felt it, too.</i>

07:44.464 --> 07:47.091
 <i>I question if Antheans</i>
 <i>ever felt it.</i>

07:47.133 --> 07:52.346
 <i>But part of me also wonders</i>
 <i>if you're fortunate not to.</i>

07:52.388 --> 07:54.098
<i>Because I've learned</i>
<i>in my time on Earth...</i>

07:54.098 --> 07:58.019
 <i>-[woman] Come, Molly!</i>
<i>- ...that joy has a price.</i>

07:58.019 --> 07:59.187
<i>Oh! </i>

08:00.271 --> 08:04.025
<i>That price is grief.</i>

08:04.066 --> 08:05.776
 <i>[monitor beeping]</i>

08:05.776 --> 08:08.196
<i>Grief is a predator.</i>

08:08.196 --> 08:09.655
<i>I couldn't have known then,</i>

08:09.655 --> 08:12.116
<i>but it was coming</i>
<i>for all of us.</i>

08:13.075 --> 08:14.827
<i>Because of me.</i>

08:26.756 --> 08:29.133
 <i>[woman vocalizing]</i>

08:37.475 --> 08:39.519
 <i>There is a concept</i>
 <i>on this planet</i>

08:39.560 --> 08:42.813
 <i>called "natural selection."</i>

08:42.855 --> 08:44.732
 <i>Meaning that variations</i>
 <i>in behavior</i>

08:44.774 --> 08:48.361
 <i>increase an organism's</i>
 <i>ability to survive...</i>

08:48.402 --> 08:49.862
<i>Or perish.</i>

08:49.862 --> 08:52.949
<i>This is particularly</i>
<i>true of humans.</i>

08:52.949 --> 08:55.743
 <i>On the far end of the spectrum</i>
 <i>are these people.</i>

08:55.743 --> 08:58.955
<i>Every generation produces</i>
<i>a small collection of minds</i>

08:58.955 --> 09:01.415
<i>that let us see</i>
<i>into new worlds.</i>

09:04.377 --> 09:05.878
<i>One of these minds</i>

09:06.504 --> 09:08.089
<i>belongs to the woman</i>

09:08.756 --> 09:10.883
 <i>Justin Falls.</i>

09:11.759 --> 09:17.932
<i>On Anthea, she would be</i>
<i>called an adept.</i>

09:17.974 --> 09:21.143
 <i>We need to go from atoms in</i>
 <i>chaos to atoms in alignment.</i>

09:21.143 --> 09:25.106
 <i>So we want a wave pattern</i>
 <i>that looks like this.</i>

09:26.023 --> 09:28.025
 <i>We need to bring</i>
 <i>the two wave functions</i>

09:28.067 --> 09:30.903
 <i>into alignment to</i>
 <i>maintain coherence.</i>

09:30.903 --> 09:33.656
 <i>I've composed an algorithm here.</i>

09:33.656 --> 09:35.866
 <i>On Earth,</i>
 <i>she theorized an algorithm</i>

09:35.908 --> 09:39.412
 <i>for fusion decades</i>
 <i>ahead of its time.</i>

09:39.412 --> 09:41.706
 <i>This is why Newton</i>
 <i>sent me to find her.</i>

09:41.747 --> 09:43.374
 <i>[Zach] Yeah, but...</i>
 <i>But this requires</i>

09:43.416 --> 09:44.709
 <i>a super computer that can do</i>

09:44.709 --> 09:47.587
 <i>a quintillion computations</i>
 <i>a second.</i>

09:47.628 --> 09:53.384
 <i>That computer doesn't exist.</i>

09:53.384 --> 09:55.469
 <i>So, we have to</i>
 <i>simplify the algorithm.</i>

09:55.511 --> 09:57.096
 <i>But if we simplify it too much,</i>

09:57.138 --> 10:00.391
 <i>the whole process becomes</i>
 <i>unstable and then...</i>

10:00.433 --> 10:02.101
 <i>[beeping]</i>

10:02.143 --> 10:03.227
 <i>[whistling]</i>

10:03.227 --> 10:04.395
 <i>Boom.</i>

10:04.687 --> 10:06.063
 <i>Boom.</i>

10:06.063 --> 10:07.940
 <i>[rumbling]</i>

10:09.775 --> 10:12.737
 <i>Gah, I hate everything.</i>
 <i>Everything.</i>

10:12.778 --> 10:14.822
 <i>The gamut of emotions</i>
 <i>humans fluctuate</i>

10:14.864 --> 10:18.784
 <i>between in the span</i>
 <i>of a day is absurd.</i>

10:18.826 --> 10:20.995
<i>Adoration, amusement, anxiety,</i>

10:20.995 --> 10:23.873
<i>awe, awkwardness,</i>
<i>bemusement, boredom,</i>

10:23.914 --> 10:26.751
<i>confusion, craving,</i>
<i>disgust, excitement,</i>

10:26.792 --> 10:28.878
<i>horror, nostalgia,</i>
<i>rage, relief,</i>

10:28.919 --> 10:32.548
<i>romance, sadness,</i>
<i>satisfaction, surprise.</i>

10:32.590 --> 10:34.759
 <i>Yes, I alphabetized.</i>

10:34.759 --> 10:37.762
 <i>Guys, if it was easy it'd be</i>
 <i>something else, right?</i>

10:37.762 --> 10:39.305
 <i>It wouldn't be fusion.</i>

10:39.639 --> 10:43.184
 <i>Fusion. We can do it.</i>

10:43.768 --> 10:46.395
 <i>Fusion. We can do it.</i>

10:46.395 --> 10:47.813
 <i>Fusion, we can do it.</i>

10:47.855 --> 10:50.483
 <i>[all chanting]</i>
 <i>Fusion, we can do it!</i>

10:51.108 --> 10:53.611
 <i>-Lucy, come on. Lucy...</i>
 <i>-Don't touch me.</i>

10:53.653 --> 10:55.529
 <i>Come on, Lucy.</i>
 <i>Fusion, we can do it!</i>

10:55.571 --> 10:57.323
 <i>[all] Fusion, we can do it!</i>

10:57.323 --> 11:00.242
 <i>All the humans around me</i>

11:00.242 --> 11:02.745
 <i>live in fear of fear.</i>

11:02.787 --> 11:05.915
 <i>So, they'll generate oxytocin</i>
 <i>or endorphins,</i>

11:05.915 --> 11:08.584
 <i>or they'll copulate,</i>
 <i>hibernate or medicate</i>

11:08.626 --> 11:12.213
 <i>in order to short circuit</i>
 <i>their fear response.</i>

11:12.213 --> 11:13.673
 <i>Fear of failure,</i>

11:13.714 --> 11:16.509
 <i>fear of loss, fear of chaos</i>

11:17.259 --> 11:21.055
 <i>causes them to lose control.</i>

11:21.055 --> 11:23.808
 <i>[Spencer] I don't understand</i>
 <i>what you're telling me, Drew.</i>

11:23.849 --> 11:26.060
<i>[Drew]</i> <i>We need to talk.</i>
<i>Face to face.</i>

11:26.060 --> 11:28.104
 <i>Now is not a good time</i>
 <i>for me to fly, okay?</i>

11:28.145 --> 11:29.355
 <i>We're actually</i>
 <i>getting somewhere.</i>

11:29.397 --> 11:32.900
 <i>I'm trying to narrow down</i>
 <i>regions on a high value target.</i>

11:32.942 --> 11:38.030
<i>I'm here, in London.</i>
<i>Tate Modern. One hour.</i>

11:38.322 --> 11:39.740
 <i>Oh, okay.</i>

11:39.782 --> 11:41.242
 <i>Okay, well, uh,</i>

11:41.283 --> 11:42.702
 <i>I'll see you there. [sighs]</i>

11:42.702 --> 11:44.662
 <i>[Lisa] There's very little room</i>
 <i>for interpretation here.</i>

11:44.662 --> 11:47.665
 <i>It's either temperate</i>
 <i>or tropical.</i>

12:00.136 --> 12:01.429
 <i>[door buzzes]</i>

12:09.520 --> 12:11.021
 <i>[Drew] I've gotta pull you out.</i>

12:11.063 --> 12:14.483
 <i>When the Security Council heard</i>
 <i>it was you, they just--</i>

12:14.525 --> 12:15.693
 <i>Me?</i>

12:16.819 --> 12:18.988
 <i>Those cocksuckers! Come on.</i>

12:18.988 --> 12:21.031
 <i>This is 'cause of</i>
 <i>what I did to that family?</i>

12:21.073 --> 12:23.492
 <i>I was working</i>
 <i>for my country, Drew.</i>

12:23.492 --> 12:25.578
 <i>-I live for my country.</i>
 <i>-I know.</i>

12:25.619 --> 12:28.330
 <i>They're doing what they do.</i>
 <i>Thinking down the line.</i>

12:28.372 --> 12:31.500
 <i>No, not one of them had</i>
 <i>the balls to do what I did.</i>

12:31.542 --> 12:32.877
 <i>That's why. Optics.</i>

12:32.877 --> 12:34.545
 <i>Optics. Optics is</i>
 <i>the whole reason</i>

12:34.587 --> 12:36.172
 <i>to keep little kids</i>
 <i>and their parents</i>

12:36.213 --> 12:37.965
 <i>-in desperate detainments. What?</i>
 <i>-What?</i>

12:37.965 --> 12:40.801
 <i>Separate detainments.</i>
 <i>You said desperate.</i>

12:40.843 --> 12:43.804
 <i>They told me to make</i>
 <i>a statement. And I did.</i>

12:43.846 --> 12:46.640
 <i>And for that I get... I get</i>
 <i>shoved in the fucking basement!</i>

12:46.640 --> 12:47.641
 <i>And now this.</i>

12:47.641 --> 12:49.894
 <i>Oh, my love, wake the fuck up.</i>

12:49.935 --> 12:53.272
 <i>You almost didn't get</i>
 <i>the basement.</i>

12:53.898 --> 12:57.276
 <i>You were out</i>
 <i>until I kept you in.</i>

12:57.318 --> 12:58.986
 <i>I know that.</i>

13:00.404 --> 13:01.989
 <i>Drew, that's a huge...</i>

13:02.865 --> 13:04.992
 <i>That's a huge part of it, okay?</i>

13:05.659 --> 13:07.703
 <i>You saved my life.</i>

13:07.745 --> 13:09.121
 <i>There's no other person alive</i>
 <i>that I would--</i>

13:09.121 --> 13:12.124
 <i>Let's save it.</i>
 <i>I know, Spence, I know.</i>

13:12.541 --> 13:13.709
 <i>You said, um...</i>

13:13.709 --> 13:16.086
 <i>[smacks lips]</i>
 <i>Let him run, right?</i>

13:16.086 --> 13:17.797
 <i>Well, I let him run. Okay?</i>

13:17.838 --> 13:19.882
 <i>And he's almost built it.</i>

13:19.882 --> 13:21.842
 <i>And it is almost ours.</i>

13:21.842 --> 13:24.845
 <i>Just give me one week. One week.</i>

13:24.887 --> 13:27.306
 <i>I have to bring him in. Me.</i>

13:28.182 --> 13:29.433
 <i>Please?</i>

13:33.312 --> 13:37.942
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Fear is tangled</i>
<i>with something called shame,</i>

13:37.942 --> 13:42.321
 <i>which seems to be their</i>
 <i>most destructive construction.</i>

13:45.866 --> 13:47.827
 <i>[shudders] My landlord says</i>

13:49.119 --> 13:51.163
 <i>I might lose my house.</i>

13:51.497 --> 13:53.457
 <i>Me. Can you believe it?</i>

13:53.499 --> 13:55.000
 <i>I've always</i>
 <i>looked after myself.</i>

13:55.042 --> 13:58.796
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Shame is fear</i>
<i>turned inward.</i>

13:58.838 --> 14:02.007
<i>Fear of what they call</i>
<i>"the self."</i>

14:02.007 --> 14:04.844
 <i>This is a concept</i>
 <i>you won't understand.</i>

14:04.885 --> 14:09.682
 <i>It means a sense of</i>
 <i>individual identity.</i>

14:10.474 --> 14:12.059
 <i>Bear with me, wife,</i>

14:12.935 --> 14:15.104
 <i>this will all connect.</i>

14:15.145 --> 14:17.815
<i>Every human has a self.</i>

14:17.857 --> 14:20.401
<i>Until now, I never did.</i>

14:20.401 --> 14:24.321
<i>On Anthea, we're born</i>
<i>as Adepts or Drones.</i>

14:24.321 --> 14:28.325
 <i>We exist only to serve</i>
 <i>the collective.</i>

14:28.367 --> 14:32.705
 <i>But here,</i>
 <i>self is something they build</i>

14:32.746 --> 14:35.332
<i>every minute, every hour.</i>

14:35.374 --> 14:37.877
<i>And as bewildering</i>
<i>as it sounds,</i>

14:37.918 --> 14:40.880
<i>they never know</i>
<i>if they're doing it right.</i>

14:40.880 --> 14:43.257
 <i>So, I've been trying to</i>
 <i>build a self.</i>

14:43.299 --> 14:46.010
 <i>Like another layer</i>
 <i>of my skin suit.</i>

14:46.051 --> 14:47.720
 <i>[Faraday on TV]</i> <i>Hello.</i>

14:47.720 --> 14:49.555
 <i>Hello.</i>

14:49.555 --> 14:51.348
<i>You look taller than me.</i>

14:51.348 --> 14:52.933
 <i>That's impossible.</i>

14:52.975 --> 14:54.685
<i>It's dinner time.</i>

14:54.685 --> 14:55.978
 <i>An affirmation of the unit</i>

14:56.020 --> 14:59.148
 <i>that restores order</i>
 <i>after a day of uncertainty.</i>

14:59.148 --> 15:00.566
<i>You're learning.</i>

15:01.859 --> 15:03.736
 <i>Let's eat.</i>

15:06.822 --> 15:08.949
 <i>[Molly] The knife</i>
 <i>is on the right,</i>

15:08.949 --> 15:11.785
 <i>right next door to the spoon.</i>

15:11.827 --> 15:14.788
 <i>The knife is on the right,</i>
 <i>right next door to the spoon.</i>

15:14.788 --> 15:16.415
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>With my new self,</i>

15:16.415 --> 15:19.418
<i>I began to anticipate</i>
<i>their rituals.</i>

15:19.460 --> 15:22.338
<i>This is the human version</i>
<i>of order.</i>

15:22.338 --> 15:25.257
 <i>You're eating six broccolis,</i>
 <i>or no screen time.</i>

15:25.299 --> 15:29.094
 <i>As if they forget they have</i>
 <i>this negotiation every day.</i>

15:29.136 --> 15:31.680
 <i>I'll throw up.</i>
 <i>I can't eat more than two.</i>

15:31.722 --> 15:34.475
 <i>Why not agree four</i>
 <i>in perpetuity?</i>

15:34.475 --> 15:35.351
 <i>-Five.</i>
 <i>-Three.</i>

15:35.351 --> 15:37.853
 <i>Okay, four. But you're</i>
 <i>eating six tomorrow.</i>

15:37.895 --> 15:40.940
 <i>-No, she's not.</i>
 <i>-No, she's not.</i>

15:43.609 --> 15:45.778
<i>And then, this again.</i>

15:45.819 --> 15:48.822
<i>It has something to do</i>
<i>with eternity.</i>

15:50.157 --> 15:52.910
<i>They believe the self exists</i>

15:52.952 --> 15:55.287
<i>in relation</i>
<i>to something bigger.</i>

15:55.329 --> 15:58.207
<i>Something they don't</i>
<i>need to see.</i>

15:58.207 --> 16:00.709
 <i>This is called faith.</i>

16:00.751 --> 16:02.294
 <i>And then work talk.</i>

16:02.294 --> 16:04.797
 <i>So, how was the lab today?</i>

16:04.797 --> 16:07.466
 <i>Oh, we're trying to make</i>
 <i>something complex</i>

16:07.466 --> 16:08.676
 <i>into something simple.</i>

16:08.676 --> 16:12.179
 <i>Like making the exact same Lego</i>
 <i>sets with less of the pieces?</i>

16:12.179 --> 16:13.514
 <i>Yeah, exactly.</i>

16:13.514 --> 16:16.100
 <i>But we haven't found</i>
 <i>the right method yet.</i>

16:16.141 --> 16:17.393
 <i>[Josiah] Have you tried</i>

16:17.393 --> 16:19.645
 <i>the Hartree-Fock</i>
 <i>mean field approach?</i>

16:19.687 --> 16:20.854
 <i>That simplified it too much.</i>

16:20.896 --> 16:24.483
 <i>Right, right,</i>
 <i>the atomic interactions would...</i>

16:24.775 --> 16:27.444
 <i>[static crackling]</i>

16:28.153 --> 16:31.365
 <i>It began just like that...</i>

16:34.410 --> 16:35.244
 <i>Uh, Dad?</i>

16:35.285 --> 16:38.330
 <i>At the time we weren't aware</i>
 <i>of its significance.</i>

16:38.372 --> 16:40.082
 <i>A small change in one state</i>

16:40.124 --> 16:42.876
 <i>of a deterministic</i>
 <i>non-linear system.</i>

16:42.918 --> 16:44.545
 <i>Dad?</i>

16:46.755 --> 16:51.510
 <i>The first crack</i>
 <i>in Josiah's self.</i>

16:53.929 --> 16:55.848
 <i>[music playing]</i>

16:56.598 --> 16:57.599
 <i>Ah...</i>

16:57.641 --> 17:02.479
 <i>Is there a moratorium against</i>
 <i>dinner music, huh?</i>

17:02.479 --> 17:03.355
 <i>Faraway!</i>

17:03.355 --> 17:06.191
 <i>You called him Faraway.</i>
 <i>It's Faraday.</i>

17:06.233 --> 17:09.445
 <i>Faraday Faraway,</i>
 <i>Faraway Faraday.</i>

17:09.486 --> 17:11.071
 <i>What do you hear?</i>

17:11.071 --> 17:13.240
 <i>This is new. A pattern change.</i>

17:13.240 --> 17:14.533
 <i>Instrumentation.</i>

17:14.575 --> 17:15.701
 <i>Expression.</i>

17:15.701 --> 17:17.703
 <i>[scatting]</i>

17:19.163 --> 17:20.873
 <i>Improvisation. [scats]</i>

17:21.790 --> 17:23.125
 <i>Everything that lives between</i>

17:23.125 --> 17:26.086
 <i>what you feel and what</i>
 <i>you can put into words.</i>

17:26.128 --> 17:29.214
 <i>On the tip of your tongue,</i>
 <i>just out of reach.</i>

17:29.256 --> 17:30.841
 <i>Silent communion.</i>

17:30.841 --> 17:31.925
 <i>Go, Dad!</i>

17:31.967 --> 17:34.053
 <i>[Josiah] Call and response.</i>

17:34.094 --> 17:37.389
 <i>This is called "theatrics."</i>

17:37.431 --> 17:39.016
<i>They wield the spotlight,</i>

17:39.058 --> 17:41.101
<i>highlighting emotion,</i>

17:41.143 --> 17:44.146
<i>emphasizing catharsis. Watch.</i>

17:44.188 --> 17:46.148
 <i>[projector whirring]</i>

17:46.190 --> 17:49.818
 <i>Don't come between me</i>
 <i>and my poetry, Miss Cynic.</i>

17:49.860 --> 17:51.070
 <i>Don't you think</i>
 <i>there's something</i>

17:51.111 --> 17:52.654
 <i>special happening here?</i>

17:52.696 --> 17:54.281
 <i>Something spiritual?</i>

17:54.281 --> 17:57.076
 <i>Listen, they don't even</i>
 <i>write that stuff down.</i>

17:57.076 --> 18:01.288
 <i>And when it's live,</i>
 <i>oh, it's transcendent.</i>

18:01.663 --> 18:03.290
 <i>Like Charlie here.</i>

18:03.332 --> 18:05.417
 <i>[playing saxophone]</i>

18:08.587 --> 18:11.298
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Improvisation</i>
<i>has one rule.</i>

18:11.799 --> 18:13.717
<i>It cannot stop.</i>

18:13.759 --> 18:15.761
 <i>Yes, there you are.</i>

18:15.761 --> 18:17.096
 <i>In a room full of people</i>

18:17.137 --> 18:20.474
 <i>that you don't even know,</i>
 <i>sharing in creation.</i>

18:22.434 --> 18:27.022
 <i>Wife, I'll now explain</i>
 <i>jazz music to you.</i>

18:27.022 --> 18:28.440
<i>It was born in America</i>

18:28.482 --> 18:29.983
<i>in the early 20th century.</i>

18:29.983 --> 18:32.569
<i>In New Orleans,</i>
<i>known as the Cradle of Jazz.</i>

18:32.611 --> 18:36.490
<i>But its true roots emerged</i>
<i>from the enslaved caste</i>

18:36.532 --> 18:40.160
<i>who brought call-and-response</i>
<i>music with them</i>

18:40.160 --> 18:42.996
<i>when they were torn</i>
<i>from their homes.</i>

18:43.038 --> 18:45.332
 <i>Call... Response.</i>

18:45.332 --> 18:49.002
<i>I'm gonna lay down</i>
<i>my burdens</i>

18:49.044 --> 18:51.630
<i>Down by the riverside</i>

18:51.630 --> 18:53.549
<i>If that mockingbird</i>
<i>don't sing</i>

18:53.549 --> 18:56.009
<i>Papa's gonna buy me</i>
<i>a diamond ring</i>

18:58.428 --> 18:59.721
<i>Happy day</i>

18:59.763 --> 19:04.351
<i>Oh, happy day</i>

19:04.393 --> 19:06.145
<i>I know a place, y'all</i>

19:06.186 --> 19:07.688
<i>I'll take you there</i>

19:07.729 --> 19:09.940
<i>- Soul power </i>  <i>- Soul power </i>

19:09.982 --> 19:13.652
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Call...</i>
<i>Response. Inseparable.</i>

19:14.069 --> 19:15.988
<i>The music of survival.</i>

19:16.029 --> 19:18.240
 <i>Impossible as it is</i>
 <i>for you to imagine,</i>

19:18.282 --> 19:20.033
 <i>it means musicians engage</i>

19:20.075 --> 19:22.077
 <i>in conversation</i>
 <i>with their instruments,</i>

19:22.077 --> 19:24.913
<i>trusting themselves</i>
<i>to play the next note</i>

19:24.955 --> 19:27.833
<i>without knowing</i>
<i>what it's supposed to be.</i>

19:27.875 --> 19:29.126
 <i>There is a word for this.</i>

19:29.168 --> 19:32.713
 <i>A variance in the science</i>
 <i>of human behavior</i>

19:32.754 --> 19:35.007
 <i>called "improvise."</i>

19:35.716 --> 19:39.511
<i>Humans have the ability</i>
<i>to improvise,</i>

19:41.680 --> 19:45.392
<i>break from pattern,</i>
<i>instantly create a new pattern,</i>

19:45.434 --> 19:48.604
<i>with no blueprint</i>
<i>and no known outcome.</i>

19:48.645 --> 19:53.025
<i>This ability</i>
<i>lived inside Josiah</i>

19:53.066 --> 19:55.611
<i>in ways I could not</i>
<i>have understood.</i>

19:55.611 --> 20:01.158
<i>If I had, this message</i>
<i>would be painless.</i>

20:11.335 --> 20:12.502
 <i>[Spencer sighs]</i>

20:12.502 --> 20:15.839
 <i>Whatever you have, it better be</i>
 <i>good enough to save your job.</i>

20:15.881 --> 20:18.217
 <i>That tornado wasn't real.</i>

20:19.301 --> 20:20.594
 <i>-What are you saying?</i>
 <i>-I mean,</i>

20:20.594 --> 20:24.223
 <i>it was real,</i>
 <i>but it didn't occur naturally.</i>

20:24.223 --> 20:26.183
 <i>There's lead and silver iodide</i>

20:26.183 --> 20:28.101
 <i>in the soil samples</i>
 <i>from the site</i>

20:28.143 --> 20:30.312
 <i>where the tornado touched down.</i>

20:30.354 --> 20:32.981
 <i>It was cloud-seeded.</i>

20:32.981 --> 20:37.194
 <i>Wait, are you suggesting that</i>
 <i>Newton made the tornado appear?</i>

20:37.236 --> 20:39.696
 <i>Well, China does it</i>
 <i>all the time to boost crops.</i>

20:39.738 --> 20:42.366
 <i>Fly a drone into the clouds,</i>
 <i>ignite a lightning storm.</i>

20:42.407 --> 20:44.868
 <i>It's weirdly</i>
 <i>pretty straightforward.</i>

20:44.868 --> 20:46.620
 <i>Oh, that is really...</i>

20:47.037 --> 20:48.914
 <i>That is really smart.</i>

20:49.289 --> 20:51.416
 <i>God damn.</i>

20:51.416 --> 20:53.293
 <i>He needed a lot of</i>
 <i>electrical interference</i>

20:53.335 --> 20:56.046
 <i>and so he created a tornado.</i>

20:56.046 --> 20:57.172
 <i>Fuck!</i>

20:57.172 --> 21:00.050
 <i>Is he dropping houses</i>
 <i>on peoples' sisters, too?</i>

21:00.050 --> 21:02.219
 <i>The bits of the signal</i>
 <i>we could track...</i>

21:02.219 --> 21:03.095
 <i>Yeah?</i>

21:03.136 --> 21:04.263
 <i>...came from somewhere</i>
 <i>in Southeast Asia.</i>

21:04.304 --> 21:06.265
 <i>We're still narrowing.</i>
 <i>There's more.</i>

21:06.306 --> 21:08.141
 <i>The flight attendant</i>
 <i>on the private plane</i>

21:08.141 --> 21:10.560
 <i>that took Faraday</i>
 <i>to the UK, Ashleigh Fiore,</i>

21:10.560 --> 21:13.105
 <i>she posted right after</i>
 <i>they landed.</i>

21:15.524 --> 21:16.942
 <i>Ashleigh Fiore.</i>

21:16.942 --> 21:19.778
 <i>Okay. Tag her phone.</i>
 <i>Send it to me.</i>

21:34.209 --> 21:36.962
 <i>There's a problem.</i>
 <i>We should meet.</i>

21:41.800 --> 21:43.093
 <i>[Hatch] Hey.</i>

21:44.094 --> 21:45.679
 <i>Aren't you an alcoholic?</i>

21:45.679 --> 21:48.849
 <i>Uh, yeah. Hence, the drinking.</i>

21:49.433 --> 21:51.059
 <i>You okay?</i>

21:51.101 --> 21:52.978
 <i>I'm fine. I'm fine.</i>

21:54.396 --> 21:55.647
 <i>How's Teddy?</i>

21:55.689 --> 21:59.860
 <i>Have you seen him</i>
 <i>since you returned?</i>

22:00.319 --> 22:01.820
 <i>No. Not yet.</i>

22:02.612 --> 22:04.865
 <i>-You never ask about Teddy.</i>
 <i>-Well...</i>

22:04.865 --> 22:07.826
 <i>I assume you didn't come here</i>
 <i>to ask me questions about...</i>

22:07.826 --> 22:09.828
 <i>Well, you lied to him.</i>
 <i>You lie to everyone,</i>

22:09.828 --> 22:12.539
 <i>so why wouldn't I assume</i>
 <i>all those years ago</i>

22:12.581 --> 22:14.291
 <i>you were lying about Newton?</i>

22:14.333 --> 22:17.336
 <i>[Hatch] Hmm. I didn't steal</i>
 <i>the fucking patent, Edie.</i>

22:18.628 --> 22:22.799
 <i>I'm not a liar.</i>
 <i>You're confusing me with Dad.</i>

22:22.799 --> 22:25.344
 <i>He had his reasons</i>
 <i>for all this, Hatch.</i>

22:25.385 --> 22:28.805
 <i>He didn't just randomly</i>
 <i>put me in charge.</i>

22:28.847 --> 22:31.683
 <i>[Hatch] I would've thought that</i>
 <i>the "alien spaceman"</i>

22:31.683 --> 22:34.353
 <i>would have inclined you</i>
 <i>in my direction a little bit.</i>

22:34.394 --> 22:36.355
 <i>The "alien spaceman" is not</i>

22:36.355 --> 22:38.648
 <i>a slate wiper</i>
 <i>for your past bullshit.</i>

22:38.648 --> 22:41.651
 <i>Edie, I hope you at least</i>
 <i>believe me when I say</i>

22:41.651 --> 22:44.112
 <i>that I don't want you</i>
 <i>to get hurt.</i>

22:44.154 --> 22:46.531
 <i>Or killed.</i>
 <i>I mean, this is the CIA.</i>

22:46.573 --> 22:47.949
 <i>They'll... They'll erase us.</i>

22:47.949 --> 22:50.702
 <i>They'll destroy Faraday's</i>
 <i>machine in the warehouse</i>

22:50.744 --> 22:52.871
 <i>before anyone ever sees it.</i>

22:54.623 --> 22:56.875
 <i>It doesn't have to be like that.</i>

22:58.126 --> 23:00.003
 <i>Pressman Thorn.</i>

23:00.003 --> 23:01.004
 <i>Thorn? Pressman Thorn?</i>

23:01.004 --> 23:04.549
 <i>[chuckles] Thorn Oil?</i>
 <i>"Melter of glaciers" Thorn?</i>

23:04.549 --> 23:07.803
 <i>I mean, he debases currencies</i>
 <i>around the world for fun.</i>

23:07.844 --> 23:10.180
 <i>He wants to add OriGen</i>
 <i>to his stable.</i>

23:10.222 --> 23:11.640
 <i>He's always been</i>
 <i>in my ear about that.</i>

23:11.681 --> 23:14.226
 <i>Edie, he's like</i>
 <i>a real-life monster.</i>

23:14.226 --> 23:15.977
 <i>This is the fastest way</i>
 <i>to get protection.</i>

23:15.977 --> 23:18.688
 <i>Who else can go to war with</i>
 <i>the CIA besides Big Oil?</i>

23:18.730 --> 23:21.316
 <i>You don't go to Big Oil</i>
 <i>to back renewable energy.</i>

23:21.358 --> 23:23.360
 <i>Thorn has the Senate</i>
 <i>Majority Leader</i>

23:23.360 --> 23:25.529
 <i>and the Intelligence</i>
 <i>Committee Chair in his pocket.</i>

23:25.529 --> 23:28.031
 <i>-He controls them.</i>
 <i>-But nobody can control him.</i>

23:28.031 --> 23:29.366
 <i>Hatch!</i>

23:30.033 --> 23:31.451
 <i>We're bleeding out.</i>

23:31.451 --> 23:33.078
 <i>You know this.</i>

23:33.662 --> 23:35.414
 <i>Without Thorn, we die.</i>

23:38.625 --> 23:40.919
 <i>I'm not asking, I'm telling.</i>

23:41.128 --> 23:42.754
 <i>I made the call.</i>

23:43.338 --> 23:44.923
 <i>We have a meeting.</i>

23:46.550 --> 23:48.260
 <i>I will need you there.</i>

23:56.017 --> 23:58.770
<i>[both]</i> <i>Grandma, Grandma</i>
<i>Sick in bed</i>

23:58.770 --> 24:01.356
<i>Called the doctor</i>
<i>and the doctor said</i>

24:01.398 --> 24:03.775
<i>Grandma, Grandma</i>
<i>You ain't sick</i>

24:03.775 --> 24:05.986
<i>What you need</i>
<i>is a walking stick</i>

24:05.986 --> 24:08.113
 <i>[Molly continues singing]</i>
<i>Get the rhythm high </i>

24:08.280 --> 24:09.906
 <i>Grandpa?</i>

24:10.991 --> 24:12.784
 <i>School's that way.</i>

24:13.577 --> 24:15.287
 <i>[guitar music playing]</i>

24:16.204 --> 24:17.789
 <i>[doorbell chiming]</i>

24:21.543 --> 24:23.253
 <i>[strums guitar]</i>

24:23.295 --> 24:25.338
 <i>-Do you play?</i>
 <i>-Barely.</i>

24:25.380 --> 24:27.132
 <i>[chuckles softly]</i>

24:27.132 --> 24:28.925
 <i>One of life's regrets.</i>

24:29.301 --> 24:31.303
 <i>-Hmm.</i>
 <i>-[strums guitar]</i>

24:33.180 --> 24:34.347
 <i>Show me a D?</i>

24:43.273 --> 24:45.108
 <i>[playing off-key]</i>

24:50.363 --> 24:52.282
 <i>[playing guitar]</i>

25:00.999 --> 25:02.167
 <i>Barely?</i>

25:05.962 --> 25:07.339
 <i>Grandpa?</i>

25:08.465 --> 25:10.008
 <i>Mm?</i>

25:13.637 --> 25:15.055
 <i>Grandpa?</i>

25:15.055 --> 25:16.973
 <i>[playing faster]</i>

25:17.349 --> 25:18.600
 <i>[moaning]</i>

25:18.600 --> 25:20.143
 <i>[string snaps]</i>

25:20.185 --> 25:21.478
 <i>[gasps]</i>

25:22.479 --> 25:23.605
 <i>[screams]</i>

25:23.647 --> 25:26.024
 <i>[siren wailing]</i>

25:31.905 --> 25:33.615
 <i>Hey, hey, hey, hey, sweetie.</i>

25:33.657 --> 25:35.534
 <i>I'm here. I'm here.</i>

25:36.201 --> 25:38.161
 <i>[breathing heavily]</i>

25:41.373 --> 25:42.999
 <i>They need to run some tests.</i>

25:42.999 --> 25:46.336
 <i>But it looks likely to</i>
 <i>have been a small stroke.</i>

25:46.836 --> 25:48.880
 <i>[Justin] It's okay.</i>

26:10.569 --> 26:14.447
 <i>Born Josiah Clarence Falls,</i>

26:14.489 --> 26:17.659
 <i>New Providence Island, Bahamas.</i>

26:17.659 --> 26:20.036
 <i>1955.</i>

26:20.078 --> 26:23.832
<i>From a young age, he focused</i>
<i>his genius on music</i>

26:23.832 --> 26:25.917
<i>and the transference of energy.</i>

26:25.959 --> 26:28.420
<i>To him, they were</i>
<i>one and the same.</i>

26:29.170 --> 26:32.257
<i>And being a genius,</i>
<i>Josiah fell in love.</i>

26:32.299 --> 26:33.675
<i>He thought he'd met the woman</i>

26:33.675 --> 26:36.261
<i>he'd spend the entirety</i>
<i>of his existence with.</i>

26:36.970 --> 26:39.431
<i>They never went to bed</i>
<i>without dancing.</i>

26:39.472 --> 26:43.435
<i>She planted bougainvillea</i>
<i>all around the house,</i>

26:43.435 --> 26:44.686
<i>threw away all his ties,</i>

26:44.728 --> 26:48.273
<i>and gave him a shave closer</i>
<i>than a barber shop.</i>

26:50.775 --> 26:53.486
<i>He could only offer a recipe</i>
<i>for conch fritters,</i>

26:53.528 --> 26:55.530
<i>and peas and rice.</i>

26:55.572 --> 26:57.657
<i>But it was enough.</i>

26:57.657 --> 26:59.784
<i>Their love produced a child,</i>

26:59.826 --> 27:01.911
<i>and the day</i>
<i>his daughter was born,</i>

27:01.911 --> 27:03.330
<i>he made her a promise.</i>

27:04.039 --> 27:06.625
 <i>[young Josiah]</i>
<i>I will live my life for you.</i>

27:16.051 --> 27:18.595
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>But Justin's mother</i>
<i>couldn't thrive</i>

27:18.595 --> 27:20.555
<i>in this new country.</i>

27:20.555 --> 27:23.933
<i>Her roots were deep</i>
<i>in her home soil.</i>

27:26.811 --> 27:29.314
<i>And on the day</i>
<i>her mother left them,</i>

27:30.148 --> 27:33.943
<i>Justin made her father</i>
<i>a promise, too.</i>

27:33.943 --> 27:37.489
<i>That she would</i>
<i>hold him forever.</i>

27:39.908 --> 27:42.035
 <i>[doctor] We'll need</i>
 <i>a neurologist to review the MRI,</i>

27:42.077 --> 27:44.621
 <i>but his previous condition</i>
 <i>has vanished.</i>

27:44.663 --> 27:46.456
 <i>It's a literal miracle.</i>

27:46.498 --> 27:48.208
 <i>He doesn't play guitar.</i>

27:49.793 --> 27:51.628
 <i>[doctor] I'd like to run</i>
 <i>some more tests.</i>

27:51.670 --> 27:54.964
 <i>University College Hospital</i>
 <i>has a research center dedi--</i>

27:54.964 --> 27:57.884
 <i>No. No, absolutely not.</i>
 <i>Thank you.</i>

27:57.884 --> 27:59.511
 <i>Angel's work.</i>

28:00.762 --> 28:02.347
 <i>Come on, Dad.</i>

28:07.394 --> 28:08.520
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Days passed</i>

28:08.520 --> 28:11.064
<i>and we were no closer</i>
<i>to simplifying the equation</i>

28:11.064 --> 28:14.025
<i>or finding an alternative</i>
<i>fuel source.</i>

28:14.025 --> 28:15.610
<i>The machine was useless.</i>

28:15.652 --> 28:17.195
 <i>[alarm beeping]</i>

28:17.821 --> 28:19.364
<i>And I was failing...</i>

28:22.325 --> 28:24.494
 <i>Again, and again.</i>

28:26.454 --> 28:27.997
 <i>-It's too high.</i>
 <i>-I know, I know.</i>

28:28.039 --> 28:29.708
 <i>-Just wait a second.</i>
 <i>-It's unstable.</i>

28:29.749 --> 28:30.959
 <i>-I know, but--</i>
 <i>-[Zach] It's too high.</i>

28:31.000 --> 28:31.960
 <i>[sound intensifies]</i>

28:31.960 --> 28:33.712
 <i>-[sound stops]</i>
 <i>-That's when I first</i>

28:33.753 --> 28:35.422
 <i>understood shame.</i>

28:36.297 --> 28:39.718
 <i>And shame became something else.</i>

28:44.889 --> 28:46.433
 <i>Why did you shut it down?</i>

28:46.433 --> 28:47.934
 <i>It's unstable.</i>

28:47.976 --> 28:49.644
 <i>The algorithm isn't simplified.</i>

28:49.686 --> 28:50.937
 <i>It's too dangerous</i>
 <i>to keep pushing.</i>

28:50.979 --> 28:53.857
 <i>You work in a laboratory. What</i>
 <i>did you think your job would be?</i>

28:53.857 --> 28:56.025
 <i>Were you told to stop?</i>

28:56.651 --> 28:58.361
 <i>Everyone out! Now.</i>

28:58.361 --> 29:00.071
 <i>You, stay.</i>

29:05.034 --> 29:06.911
 <i>What do you mean</i>
 <i>you optimized him?</i>

29:06.911 --> 29:09.080
 <i>I gave him some of my DNA.</i>

29:09.372 --> 29:10.290
 <i>What?</i>

29:10.331 --> 29:13.126
 <i>The dominance of the transfusion</i>
 <i>is rewriting his genetic code.</i>

29:13.126 --> 29:16.588
 <i>The... The dominance</i>
 <i>of the transfusion...</i>

29:17.338 --> 29:18.673
 <i>My dad is becoming--</i>

29:18.673 --> 29:20.175
 <i>I cannot confirm</i>
 <i>what he is becoming.</i>

29:20.175 --> 29:21.426
 <i>I can confirm</i>
 <i>that we are failing.</i>

29:21.426 --> 29:25.597
 <i>Guys. So, I've got Lucy</i>
 <i>in my office screaming at me.</i>

29:25.597 --> 29:27.599
 <i>She terminated</i>
 <i>an experiment in process.</i>

29:27.640 --> 29:28.767
 <i>[Justin] Shut up about Lucy!</i>

29:28.808 --> 29:31.853
 <i>My father,</i>
 <i>something is happening to him,</i>

29:31.895 --> 29:33.772
 <i>and it is not a fucking stroke.</i>

29:33.813 --> 29:35.899
 <i>Perhaps he is between gears.</i>

29:35.940 --> 29:37.734
 <i>What gears?</i>

29:38.276 --> 29:39.277
 <i>What is he turning into?</i>

29:39.319 --> 29:41.863
 <i>I fixed him. He's likely</i>
 <i>to live longer than you.</i>

29:41.863 --> 29:42.947
 <i>You... You fixed him?</i>

29:42.947 --> 29:44.824
 <i>I don't recognize him.</i>

29:44.824 --> 29:46.493
 <i>I eliminated his analog space.</i>

29:46.534 --> 29:49.037
 <i>His representational space.</i>

29:49.078 --> 29:50.580
 <i>That space was him!</i>

29:50.622 --> 29:52.373
 <i>This is not what is</i>
 <i>important right now!</i>

29:52.373 --> 29:53.249
 <i>[Hatch] All right. Stop.</i>

29:53.291 --> 29:54.876
 <i>Listen, whatever's wrong</i>
 <i>with your dad,</i>

29:54.918 --> 29:56.085
 <i>it sounds like</i>
 <i>he needs a doctor.</i>

29:56.127 --> 29:58.755
 <i>-We just came from a doctor.</i>
 <i>-A doctor we can trust.</i>

30:00.507 --> 30:01.674
 <i>This I can do.</i>

30:03.009 --> 30:05.011
 <i>Okay, Zach, lay some skin on me.</i>

30:05.011 --> 30:07.639
 <i>-[chuckles] See you.</i>
 <i>-[Zach] Bye, Dr. Sloane.</i>

30:13.520 --> 30:15.980
 <i>You show up here like... Like...</i>

30:16.022 --> 30:18.900
 <i>-Like...</i>
 <i>-Teddy, I'm sorry.</i>

30:18.942 --> 30:21.277
 <i>[scoffs] Sorry?</i>

30:22.821 --> 30:24.614
 <i>[stammers] Uh, is that it?</i>

30:24.656 --> 30:27.534
 <i>Two syllables</i>
 <i>to replace three years</i>

30:27.575 --> 30:30.662
 <i>of grief, anger and resentment.</i>

30:30.662 --> 30:33.289
 <i>I have more syllables</i>
 <i>if you'll hear them.</i>

30:35.041 --> 30:38.127
 <i>Right now? Okay.</i>

30:38.169 --> 30:40.129
 <i>As you know, I was fired,</i>

30:40.129 --> 30:43.633
 <i>and excommunicated</i>
 <i>and emotionally extradited--</i>

30:43.675 --> 30:45.468
 <i>-Hatch, I have work to do.</i>
 <i>-I fucked up.</i>

30:45.468 --> 30:49.138
 <i>I was ashamed and I wanted</i>
 <i>to die. So, I ran away.</i>

30:49.597 --> 30:51.307
 <i>And you're here now</i>
 <i>for what?</i>

30:53.101 --> 30:55.228
 <i>I need you to look at something.</i>

30:55.687 --> 30:57.063
 <i>And, um...</i>

30:57.105 --> 31:01.025
 <i>And I never stopped</i>
 <i>wanting to see you again.</i>

31:01.025 --> 31:03.903
 <i>Look, fine,</i>
 <i>I'm an asshole, all right?</i>

31:03.903 --> 31:06.489
 <i>We know that.</i>
 <i>But... this isn't about me.</i>

31:06.531 --> 31:07.532
 <i>Pretend I'm a stranger.</i>

31:07.574 --> 31:09.325
 <i>This is about a man's life.</i>

31:09.325 --> 31:12.370
 <i>And a family.</i>
 <i>An innocent family.</i>

31:26.885 --> 31:29.387
 <i>Dystonia doesn't get better.</i>

31:29.679 --> 31:30.889
 <i>Exactly.</i>

31:31.556 --> 31:33.391
 <i>Hatch, what is this?</i>

31:34.851 --> 31:38.730
 <i>It's more alien stuff.</i>

31:40.523 --> 31:44.027
<i>Can I have a taste</i>
<i>of your ice cream?</i>

31:44.068 --> 31:47.655
<i>Can I lick the crumbs</i>
<i>from your table?</i>

31:47.697 --> 31:51.200
<i>Can I interfere</i>
<i>in your crisis?</i>

31:51.200 --> 31:54.454
<i>No, mind your own business</i>

31:54.954 --> 31:57.832
<i>No, mind your own business </i>

31:57.874 --> 31:59.125
 <i>[panting]</i>

31:59.125 --> 32:01.586
 <i>[music playing indistinctly</i>
 <i>over earbuds]</i>

32:06.424 --> 32:07.884
 <i>[Spencer] What are you</i>
 <i>listening to?</i>

32:07.884 --> 32:09.218
 <i>What?</i>

32:10.136 --> 32:12.096
 <i>Sorry, I was just asking</i>
 <i>what you're listening to.</i>

32:12.096 --> 32:14.098
 <i>It's Ashleigh, isn't it?</i>

32:14.140 --> 32:16.225
 <i>Yeah, Ashleigh.</i>
 <i>But not with a "Y,"</i>

32:16.225 --> 32:19.604
 <i>with, uh, "E-I-G-H,"</i>
 <i>like "sleigh."</i>

32:20.188 --> 32:22.440
 <i>No, I don't know you. Fuck off.</i>

32:22.482 --> 32:23.942
 <i>How about that?</i>

32:23.942 --> 32:25.860
 <i>You've seen a badge</i>
 <i>before, right?</i>

32:25.860 --> 32:27.153
 <i>You wanna hold it?</i>

32:27.153 --> 32:28.571
 <i>No, thank you.</i>

32:29.280 --> 32:32.033
 <i>Okay, Ashleigh. "E-I-G-H."</i>

32:32.033 --> 32:35.620
 <i>No, um, yes.</i>
 <i>"E-I-G-H" like "sleigh."</i>

32:35.620 --> 32:37.288
 <i>I should put bells on you.</i>

32:39.082 --> 32:40.792
 <i>You could be my reindeer.</i>

32:41.250 --> 32:42.794
 <i>Guess that would make me Santa.</i>

32:44.796 --> 32:47.298
 <i>You want me to put</i>
 <i>reins in your mouth, Ashleigh?</i>

32:48.758 --> 32:50.969
 <i>-No.</i>
 <i>-Come here.</i>

32:51.594 --> 32:53.054
 <i>-No.</i>
 <i>-Come here,</i>

32:53.054 --> 32:55.556
 <i>Ashleigh Fiore,</i>
 <i>364 Maron Drive.</i>

32:55.556 --> 32:56.975
 <i>Daughter to Henry.</i>

32:57.892 --> 33:00.979
 <i>Sister to Brinleigh.</i>

33:01.020 --> 33:03.815
 <i>She does the "E-I-G-H," too,</i>
 <i>doesn't she, Ash?</i>

33:06.651 --> 33:08.111
 <i>So, on your Instagram, um...</i>

33:08.152 --> 33:11.447
 <i>[smacks lips] Uh, uh, the jet.</i>
 <i>The day that you called,</i>

33:11.447 --> 33:12.865
 <i>"Fucking whacked"?</i>

33:12.907 --> 33:16.077
 <i>There was a guy.</i>
 <i>There was a really weird guy.</i>

33:16.119 --> 33:17.829
 <i>On the plane, remember?</i>

33:20.540 --> 33:22.917
 <i>-NDA.</i>
 <i>-CIA.</i>

33:22.917 --> 33:24.836
 <i>Well, I know</i>
 <i>you're a pack animal.</i>

33:24.836 --> 33:26.045
 <i>I know you're a beast of burden,</i>

33:26.087 --> 33:27.797
 <i>but you can tell me</i>
 <i>what you saw on the jet</i>

33:27.839 --> 33:29.298
 <i>or I'll have you</i>
 <i>charged with treason.</i>

33:29.298 --> 33:32.677
 <i>And I'll stick you in a room</i>
 <i>with reins in your mouth</i>

33:32.677 --> 33:34.512
 <i>for the rest of your life.</i>

33:36.014 --> 33:37.306
 <i>Talk to me.</i>

33:37.348 --> 33:40.810
 <i>He asked if the cabin</i>
 <i>was pressurized.</i>

33:41.936 --> 33:42.812
 <i>[Spencer] What?</i>

33:42.854 --> 33:44.981
 <i>He asked if the cabin</i>
 <i>was pressurized.</i>

33:44.981 --> 33:46.733
 <i>Why? Why did he do that?</i>

33:49.235 --> 33:54.365
 <i>He kind of...</i>
 <i>He kind of got like... That.</i>

33:57.827 --> 33:59.871
 <i>-The balloons?</i>
 <i>-Yeah.</i>

34:02.373 --> 34:05.126
 <i>It's about gravity or...</i>
 <i>Or air pressure.</i>

34:05.126 --> 34:06.544
 <i>And maybe that's why</i>
 <i>he didn't want the lab</i>

34:06.586 --> 34:08.921
 <i>on the third floor,</i>
 <i>because of the elevators.</i>

34:08.921 --> 34:10.131
 <i>You think to survive long-term</i>

34:10.173 --> 34:11.841
 <i>they need</i>
 <i>a low gravity location?</i>

34:11.841 --> 34:14.385
<i>[Spencer]</i> <i>High altitude.</i>
<i>Low oxygen.</i>

34:15.053 --> 34:17.555
 <i>I think it's about</i>
 <i>how thin the air is.</i>

34:18.681 --> 34:20.266
 <i>Check mountain ranges.</i>

34:26.898 --> 34:28.900
 <i>[blues music playing]</i>

34:35.948 --> 34:37.408
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>I searched</i>
<i>Newton's old work</i>

34:37.450 --> 34:39.619
<i>for something</i>
<i>I must have overlooked.</i>

34:39.619 --> 34:42.080
<i>I got ramblin'</i>

34:43.164 --> 34:46.626
<i>I got ramblin' on my mind </i>

34:50.338 --> 34:51.506
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Some hidden detail</i>

34:51.506 --> 34:53.591
<i>that would lead me</i>
<i>to a solution.</i>

34:54.008 --> 34:56.094
<i>Hate to leave my baby</i>

34:57.178 --> 34:59.931
<i>But you treat me so unkind </i>

34:59.931 --> 35:01.766
 <i>[high-pitched whining]</i>

35:04.811 --> 35:06.437
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>But I was lost.</i>

35:18.324 --> 35:19.826
 <i>[siren wailing]</i>

35:25.206 --> 35:27.625
<i>Why the impossible science?</i>

35:29.127 --> 35:32.338
<i>Why the instruction</i>
<i>"to see with their eyes"?</i>

35:34.173 --> 35:36.926
<i>Why this journey into self?</i>

35:37.802 --> 35:40.012
<i>My mind began to fracture.</i>

35:44.225 --> 35:46.894
 <i>Until then, I had only</i>
 <i>perceived our existence</i>

35:46.936 --> 35:49.689
 <i>through a singular</i>
 <i>point of view.</i>

35:49.689 --> 35:51.816
<i>With a singular purpose.</i>

35:52.942 --> 35:55.653
 <i>To protect the hive.</i>

36:12.253 --> 36:14.672
 <i>[bees buzzing]</i>

36:18.259 --> 36:19.886
 <i>[horns honking]</i>

36:19.886 --> 36:21.012
 <i>[engine revs]</i>

36:21.637 --> 36:22.722
 <i>[tires screech]</i>

36:22.763 --> 36:24.140
 <i>[horns honking]</i>

36:25.099 --> 36:28.728
 <i>He's okay. Just confused,</i>
 <i>frustrated. He's inside.</i>

36:28.728 --> 36:30.062
 <i>Yeah, thanks.</i>

36:31.939 --> 36:34.817
 <i>[Josiah] Six, three,</i>
 <i>seven, eight, two...</i>

36:36.277 --> 36:37.320
 <i>[Justin] Dad?</i>

36:37.320 --> 36:40.114
 <i>[Josiah] Zero, two, four,</i>
 <i>six, seven, one.</i>

36:40.114 --> 36:42.575
 <i>-If you undid it and...</i>
 <i>-Molly, stay... Stay here.</i>

36:42.575 --> 36:43.993
 <i>...and then you look at it...</i>

36:44.035 --> 36:46.329
 <i>Why? Why is it stuck?</i>
 <i>Why is it stuck?</i>

36:46.370 --> 36:48.164
 <i>Molly, go to your room.</i>

36:48.164 --> 36:50.291
 <i>-[mumbling]</i>
 <i>-Dad? Dad?</i>

36:50.291 --> 36:52.418
 <i>Seven...</i>
 <i>Where's the seventh?</i>

36:52.418 --> 36:56.380
 <i>Hey, hey, hey. It's me.</i>
 <i>It's me, Juzzie.</i>

36:56.380 --> 36:59.759
 <i>It's me, Dad. It's Juzzie.</i>
 <i>Yeah. Yeah.</i>

36:59.800 --> 37:01.677
 <i>-Juzzie?</i>
 <i>-Yeah.</i>

37:02.053 --> 37:03.512
 <i>Juzzie?</i>

37:04.388 --> 37:05.848
 <i>[exhales]</i>

37:05.890 --> 37:07.516
 <i>What's happening to me?</i>

37:09.727 --> 37:11.562
 <i>[breathing heavily]</i>

37:11.979 --> 37:13.814
 <i>Come here, Dad.</i>

37:13.814 --> 37:15.900
 <i>-[cries]</i>
 <i>-It's gonna be okay.</i>

37:19.654 --> 37:21.030
 <i>[crying]</i>

37:25.117 --> 37:27.536
 <i>-[Hatch] Thanks for comin'.</i>
 <i>-[Teddy] Uh-huh.</i>

37:46.347 --> 37:48.724
 <i>Looks like you've got</i>
 <i>something on your mind.</i>

37:54.063 --> 37:55.690
 <i>[clicks tongue] Okay.</i>

37:55.690 --> 37:59.151
 <i>Physically he is like</i>
 <i>a 40-year-old triathlete.</i>

37:59.193 --> 38:02.405
 <i>His blood oxygen levels</i>
 <i>are abnormally high.</i>

38:02.446 --> 38:03.572
 <i>I'll keep an eye on that.</i>

38:03.614 --> 38:05.658
 <i>But he's not in</i>
 <i>any danger in that way.</i>

38:05.700 --> 38:10.079
 <i>His file reads like,</i>
 <i>uh, fantasy.</i>

38:10.079 --> 38:13.291
 <i>He... He is a miracle.</i>

38:13.291 --> 38:17.003
 <i>Beyond that,</i>
 <i>it's for a psychiatrist.</i>

38:17.044 --> 38:19.255
 <i>-I, um--</i>
 <i>-[Teddy] I understand.</i>

38:19.297 --> 38:21.757
 <i>You can't bring him</i>
 <i>to other doctors.</i>

38:21.757 --> 38:26.804
 <i>Well, I'm here for you</i>
 <i>and you can call me anytime.</i>

38:27.805 --> 38:29.265
 <i>Thank you.</i>

38:36.522 --> 38:39.650
 <i>Hey. Uh, Teddy, before you go,</i>
 <i>I wanted to--</i>

38:39.650 --> 38:41.360
 <i>Shut up.</i>

38:41.402 --> 38:43.654
 <i>You've been given</i>
 <i>a responsibility.</i>

38:44.238 --> 38:45.323
 <i>I don't even think</i>
 <i>you understand</i>

38:45.323 --> 38:47.033
 <i>how massive</i>
 <i>the responsibility is.</i>

38:47.074 --> 38:49.118
 <i>Uh. Well, I... I think I do.</i>

38:49.118 --> 38:51.829
 <i>-Ah.</i>
 <i>-Do you wanna meet the guy who--</i>

38:52.538 --> 38:54.457
 <i>I don't wanna meet anybody else.</i>

38:54.498 --> 38:56.667
 <i>I don't wanna know</i>
 <i>any more than I have to.</i>

38:57.501 --> 39:00.212
 <i>Don't fuck this one up,</i>
 <i>Hatch. Huh?</i>

39:00.212 --> 39:03.007
 <i>If you fuck this one up,</i>
 <i>it's an actual sin.</i>

39:07.094 --> 39:08.471
 <i>My dad almost got killed</i>

39:08.471 --> 39:11.098
 <i>in the middle of the road</i>
 <i>listening to fucking bees.</i>

39:11.098 --> 39:13.142
 <i>[Josiah] Zero, eight, zero...</i>

39:13.142 --> 39:14.435
 <i>Bees?</i>

39:14.477 --> 39:17.938
 <i>What you call bees, we have</i>
 <i>a very similar species at home.</i>

39:17.980 --> 39:19.148
 <i>And?</i>

39:19.690 --> 39:22.318
 <i>Antheans hold them, bees,</i>

39:22.360 --> 39:24.487
 <i>in high regards</i>
 <i>for their efficiency</i>

39:24.528 --> 39:27.031
 <i>and singularity of purpose.</i>

39:27.031 --> 39:29.033
 <i>-Dad.</i>
 <i>-No! No! [grunts]</i>

39:29.492 --> 39:31.535
 <i>This is not my father.</i>

39:31.577 --> 39:33.662
 <i>[Josiah mumbling]</i>

39:33.704 --> 39:36.248
 <i>[Josiah] Nine, eight, seven,</i>
 <i>two, one.</i>

39:36.290 --> 39:37.875
 <i>Don't! [grunts]</i>

39:38.793 --> 39:40.002
 <i>Dad.</i>

39:40.002 --> 39:41.212
 <i>[grunts]</i>

39:42.463 --> 39:44.048
 <i>[breathing heavily]</i>

39:44.048 --> 39:45.341
 <i>[Josiah] Five, six, four, one...</i>

39:45.341 --> 39:46.300
 <i>Get out!</i>

39:46.342 --> 39:48.010
 <i>You did this to him.</i>

39:48.010 --> 39:49.512
 <i>Get the fuck out now!</i>

39:49.512 --> 39:51.597
 <i>[Josiah] ...two, two.</i>

39:55.101 --> 39:57.228
 <i>[muttering]</i>

39:57.686 --> 39:59.230
 <i>[breathing heavily]</i>

40:03.067 --> 40:05.444
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>She was right.</i>

40:05.444 --> 40:09.115
<i>But even then, I couldn't</i>
<i>comprehend what I had done.</i>

40:10.741 --> 40:14.537
<i>"I showed the grown-ups</i>
<i>my masterpiece</i>

40:14.537 --> 40:17.915
<i>"and I asked them</i>
<i>if my drawings scared them.</i>

40:18.499 --> 40:22.753
<i>"They answered,</i>
<i>'Why be scared of a hat?'</i>

40:23.504 --> 40:26.257
<i>"My drawing was not</i>
<i>a picture of a hat.</i>

40:27.508 --> 40:30.261
<i>"It was a picture</i>
<i>of a boa constrictor</i>

40:30.261 --> 40:32.304
<i>"digesting an elephant."</i>

40:32.346 --> 40:33.973
 <i>A gift from a child.</i>

40:34.765 --> 40:37.768
 <i>A story about perspective...</i>

40:42.690 --> 40:44.775
<i>And transformation.</i>

40:52.658 --> 40:54.743
<i>I was looking</i>
<i>at the machine one way.</i>

40:54.743 --> 40:57.621
<i>Josiah was looking</i>
<i>at it another.</i>

40:57.621 --> 40:59.415
<i>Or from</i>
<i>a different perspective,</i>

40:59.457 --> 41:03.294
<i>the machine was calling to us.</i>

41:04.545 --> 41:07.423
 <i>Call, response.</i>

41:08.048 --> 41:09.592
<i>I was responding one way.</i>

41:09.633 --> 41:12.428
<i>Josiah was responding another.</i>

41:12.428 --> 41:15.347
 <i>Expression. Improvisation.</i>

41:15.389 --> 41:17.850
<i>Everything that lives</i>
<i>between what you feel</i>

41:17.850 --> 41:19.685
 <i>and what you can put into words.</i>

41:19.685 --> 41:23.314
 <i>Tip of your tongue,</i>
 <i>just out of reach.</i>

41:24.106 --> 41:26.150
 <i>Nine, six.</i>

41:27.026 --> 41:29.278
 <i>[birds chirping]</i>

41:40.873 --> 41:42.583
<i>Don't you think</i>
<i>there's something</i>

41:42.625 --> 41:44.335
<i>special happening here?</i>

41:44.627 --> 41:46.670
 <i>Something spiritual.</i>

41:52.134 --> 41:54.011
 <i>It's transcendent.</i>

42:08.859 --> 42:11.195
 <i>Is he gonna get better?</i>

42:12.613 --> 42:14.114
 <i>Yeah, I don't...</i>

42:14.156 --> 42:16.075
 <i>I don't know, baby.</i>

42:16.116 --> 42:19.495
 <i>But, um, you know...</i>

42:19.495 --> 42:22.289
 <i>We got the gift</i>
 <i>of this time with him.</i>

42:22.289 --> 42:23.374
 <i>And he was...</i>

42:23.415 --> 42:24.792
 <i>He was happy in a way that--</i>

42:24.792 --> 42:27.127
 <i>That sounds like you think</i>
 <i>he's gonna die.</i>

42:27.169 --> 42:28.379
 <i>No.</i>

42:29.129 --> 42:30.881
 <i>No, no, no, I don't.</i>

42:32.508 --> 42:34.343
 <i>I'm ju-- [sniffles]</i>

42:34.843 --> 42:37.179
 <i>Well, I'm scared, too.</i>

42:41.642 --> 42:43.227
 <i>[doorbell ringing]</i>

42:47.147 --> 42:48.607
 <i>He had your equation.</i>

42:48.649 --> 42:50.192
 <i>He's trying to communicate.</i>

42:50.234 --> 42:51.360
 <i>It doesn't have</i>
 <i>to be interpreted</i>

42:51.402 --> 42:52.444
 <i>as electromagnetic waves.</i>

42:52.444 --> 42:56.574
 <i>The bees, the guitar,</i>
 <i>the waves are sound.</i>

43:02.746 --> 43:04.915
 <i>They're frequencies.</i>

43:10.546 --> 43:15.050
 <i>Substitute sound waves</i>
 <i>for electromagnetic waves.</i>

43:15.092 --> 43:18.095
 <i>They'll make the atoms</i>
 <i>work in harmony.</i>

43:18.095 --> 43:20.639
<i>[Faraday]</i> <i>The way bees</i>
<i>work in harmony.</i>

43:20.639 --> 43:24.143
 <i>We needed a super computer</i>
 <i>powerful enough to align atoms.</i>

43:24.184 --> 43:27.896
 <i>That super computer is jazz.</i>

43:29.732 --> 43:33.611
 <i>Josiah converted his daughter's</i>
 <i>equation into sound frequencies.</i>

43:33.652 --> 43:36.947
<i>Because music itself</i>
<i>is mathematical.</i>

43:36.947 --> 43:41.118
 <i>He simplified the equation</i>
 <i>and wrote us</i>

43:41.452 --> 43:43.120
 <i>the song.</i>

43:45.581 --> 43:47.458
 <i>[piano music playing]</i>

43:49.001 --> 43:51.503
 <i>[Justin] If the lights turn on,</i>
 <i>we know we have energy.</i>

43:51.503 --> 43:54.381
 <i>If the lights turn pink,</i>
 <i>we know it's stable.</i>

43:54.381 --> 43:56.175
 <i>-Hmm.</i>
 <i>-Dad...</i>

43:56.216 --> 43:57.509
 <i>-Hmm.</i>
 <i>-Mm-hmm.</i>

44:01.889 --> 44:04.308
 <i>Okay. Here you go.</i>

44:04.850 --> 44:06.644
 <i>It's what you wrote on the wall.</i>

44:06.644 --> 44:08.854
 <i>[Josiah breathing heavily]</i>

44:17.988 --> 44:20.699
 <i>[Justin] Capacitor bank's</i>
 <i>fully charged.</i>

44:20.741 --> 44:22.368
 <i>Safety's enabled.</i>

44:23.077 --> 44:24.370
 <i>Ready to fire.</i>

44:24.370 --> 44:28.332
 <i>-In three, two, one.</i>
 <i>-[beeps]</i>

44:29.124 --> 44:30.542
 <i>[hissing]</i>

44:40.928 --> 44:42.971
 <i>[computer beeping]</i>

44:46.767 --> 44:48.394
 <i>Plasma is stable.</i>

44:48.811 --> 44:50.354
 <i>The density is good.</i>

44:50.396 --> 44:51.814
 <i>[Justin] Ready for heating.</i>

44:51.814 --> 44:53.691
 <i>If my dad has</i>
 <i>any problems at all,</i>

44:53.691 --> 44:57.361
 <i>you shut it down. I don't care</i>
 <i>how close we are. Okay?</i>

45:04.284 --> 45:05.994
 <i>You ready, Dad?</i>

45:11.375 --> 45:12.584
 <i>[plays note]</i>

45:30.644 --> 45:32.271
 <i>[continues playing]</i>

45:36.233 --> 45:37.735
 <i>[powering up]</i>

45:42.740 --> 45:44.575
 <i>Acceleration's not stable.</i>

45:44.867 --> 45:46.952
 <i>Shit. It's slowing down.</i>

45:49.705 --> 45:51.248
 <i>[Hatch] Is slow bad?</i>

45:51.248 --> 45:53.250
 <i>-Faster.</i>
 <i>-Carefully.</i>

45:53.292 --> 45:55.210
 <i>[continues playing notes]</i>

45:58.797 --> 46:01.592
 <i>Dad, try a higher frequency.</i>

46:02.885 --> 46:04.636
 <i>[plays higher notes]</i>

46:15.731 --> 46:17.399
 <i>It's destructing.</i>
 <i>Shut it down, shut it down!</i>

46:17.399 --> 46:22.154
 <i>No. No, keep going. The rule of</i>
 <i>improvisation is it cannot stop.</i>

46:22.196 --> 46:25.783
 <i>All right. Give me, uh,</i>
 <i>10% more at the top.</i>

46:26.366 --> 46:27.743
 <i>Higher amplitude.</i>

46:27.785 --> 46:29.077
 <i>[continues playing notes]</i>

46:29.119 --> 46:30.788
 <i>A bit more in the middle.</i>

46:35.000 --> 46:37.586
 <i>No, no, no.</i>
 <i>That's too much. Half that.</i>

46:37.628 --> 46:39.421
 <i>[continues playing notes]</i>

46:42.382 --> 46:44.426
 <i>Do that again. That same phrase.</i>

46:56.104 --> 46:57.773
 <i>That's the resonance.</i>

46:57.940 --> 46:59.066
 <i>Okay.</i>

46:59.066 --> 47:01.985
 <i>Keep it going. Keep it going.</i>

47:04.613 --> 47:06.156
 <i>[music continues]</i>

47:32.432 --> 47:34.852
 <i>[powering up]</i>

47:34.852 --> 47:36.812
 <i>What's happening here?</i>

47:36.812 --> 47:38.730
 <i>[laughs]</i>

47:38.772 --> 47:41.400
 <i>We just taught a computer jazz.</i>

47:44.027 --> 47:46.196
 <i>Now we see if it can play.</i>

48:37.831 --> 48:39.458
 <i>[Justin] Dad.</i>

48:39.458 --> 48:41.043
 <i>Dad, you did it.</i>

48:41.084 --> 48:43.962
 <i>You did it, you did it,</i>
 <i>you did it.</i>

48:43.962 --> 48:45.756
 <i>[sniffles]</i>

49:25.796 --> 49:27.589
 <i>Doctor, hi.</i>

49:27.589 --> 49:29.508
 <i>[Teddy] Sorry, do I know--</i>

49:29.508 --> 49:30.842
 <i>Ah! [grunting]</i>

49:30.842 --> 49:32.010
 <i>[screams] No!</i>

49:32.052 --> 49:35.806
 <i>The file for Josiah Falls. Now.</i>

49:37.307 --> 49:38.725
 <i>[Spencer] They fucking</i>
 <i>turned it on?</i>

49:38.725 --> 49:39.810
 <i>Why didn't you</i>
 <i>tell me immediately?</i>

49:39.851 --> 49:41.144
 <i>[Lisa] It's the middle</i>
 <i>of the night.</i>

49:41.186 --> 49:43.230
 <i>By the time Tim got me,</i>
 <i>it was over.</i>

49:43.230 --> 49:44.690
 <i>Why were you away</i>
 <i>from your phone?</i>

49:44.731 --> 49:46.650
 <i>I found Newton.</i>

49:47.025 --> 49:47.943
 <i>What? What? How?</i>

49:47.985 --> 49:49.987
 <i>-I got Josiah's medical files.</i>
 <i>-Okay.</i>

49:50.028 --> 49:52.614
 <i>[Lisa] I checked the hemoglobin</i>
 <i>levels in his blood work.</i>

49:52.656 --> 49:54.116
 <i>Their blood needs</i>
 <i>twice the oxygen.</i>

49:54.157 --> 49:56.994
 <i>That means they need</i>
 <i>dense vegetation.</i>

49:56.994 --> 49:58.286
 <i>And we know we're looking for</i>

49:58.286 --> 50:00.414
 <i>mountain ranges</i>
 <i>in Southeast Asia.</i>

50:00.414 --> 50:02.874
 <i>We are looking for</i>
 <i>elevated jungles.</i>

50:02.874 --> 50:05.002
 <i>What are you telling me?</i>
 <i>Where is he? Where is he?</i>

50:06.003 --> 50:07.504
 <i>Cambodia.</i>

50:07.963 --> 50:10.048
 <i>He's in Cambodia.</i>

50:10.048 --> 50:11.383
 <i>What is this? What is this mass?</i>

50:11.425 --> 50:13.719
 <i>[Lisa] Two hundred thousand</i>
 <i>tons of cement.</i>

50:13.760 --> 50:15.595
 <i>In the middle of the jungle.</i>

50:15.595 --> 50:16.638
 <i>That could be a lot of things.</i>

50:16.638 --> 50:17.889
 <i>It could be a silo,</i>
 <i>it could be a dam.</i>

50:17.931 --> 50:19.683
 <i>It's underground.</i>

50:20.642 --> 50:22.519
 <i>Oh, shit. Newton's...</i>

50:22.561 --> 50:25.355
 <i>-Newton's in a bunker.</i>
 <i>-[chuckles softly]</i>

50:31.236 --> 50:33.363
 <i>Wow, that is a terrible car.</i>

50:34.072 --> 50:38.577
 <i>Awful. Hey, congratulations.</i>

50:38.994 --> 50:39.953
 <i>Thank you.</i>

50:39.995 --> 50:42.247
 <i>I mean, it is never</i>
 <i>leaving the building, but...</i>

50:42.247 --> 50:44.541
 <i>Why are you</i>
 <i>so fucking brazen?</i>

50:45.125 --> 50:47.210
 <i>I just saw a miracle.</i>

50:47.252 --> 50:48.336
 <i>Hold on. Is this that moment</i>

50:48.378 --> 50:49.880
 <i>where the miracle</i>
 <i>finally wins out?</i>

50:49.921 --> 50:51.381
 <i>Yeah, you know what?</i>
 <i>I feel like, it is.</i>

50:51.423 --> 50:53.925
 <i>Then you're a child. I have it.</i>

50:53.925 --> 50:55.218
 <i>Hatch, I have you.</i>

50:55.218 --> 50:57.345
 <i>I feel like you had me</i>
 <i>a little better</i>

50:57.345 --> 50:59.890
 <i>before the fucking</i>
 <i>machine worked.</i>

51:00.098 --> 51:01.141
 <i>You psycho!</i>

51:01.183 --> 51:04.561
 <i>You know... You know what</i>
 <i>I absolutely have, Hatch?</i>

51:06.146 --> 51:07.939
 <i>I have proof</i>

51:07.939 --> 51:09.816
 <i>that you smuggled</i>
 <i>Newton's tenth design</i>

51:09.816 --> 51:10.984
 <i>out of OriGen seven years ago.</i>

51:10.984 --> 51:12.736
 <i>And that you tried to sell it.</i>

51:12.778 --> 51:14.488
 <i>And to whom.</i>

51:14.488 --> 51:19.367
 <i>Okay? So, this shit you're</i>
 <i>spraying about a miracle,</i>

51:19.367 --> 51:21.536
 <i>that miracle had</i>
 <i>a price tag for you.</i>

51:21.578 --> 51:25.540
 <i>That included the fact that</i>
 <i>you betrayed your sister.</i>

51:26.249 --> 51:27.292
 <i>Didn't you?</i>

51:27.334 --> 51:31.588
 <i>Your steely and fragile sister.</i>

51:34.049 --> 51:35.592
 <i>Now that you're all</i>
 <i>rebonded again,</i>

51:35.634 --> 51:39.721
 <i>it would be a fucking shame</i>
 <i>if she found out.</i>

51:54.820 --> 51:59.449
<i>[Justin]</i> <i>He's changing into</i>
<i>something Anthean. Isn't he?</i>

52:04.204 --> 52:05.956
 <i>When I realigned him,</i>

52:07.165 --> 52:09.584
 <i>I was trying to unburden you.</i>

52:12.212 --> 52:13.922
 <i>The burden is love.</i>

52:17.259 --> 52:19.427
 <i>You don't understand.</i>

52:21.304 --> 52:22.806
 <i>I'm starting to.</i>

52:26.017 --> 52:27.936
 <i>You were...</i>

52:27.936 --> 52:29.813
 <i>You were trying to</i>
 <i>help the mission.</i>

52:31.690 --> 52:32.983
 <i>Help yourself.</i>

52:34.359 --> 52:35.819
 <i>Help him, too.</i>

52:42.367 --> 52:44.452
 <i>I'm sorry I yelled at you.</i>

52:46.037 --> 52:47.831
 <i>This wouldn't have happened</i>

52:48.790 --> 52:50.500
 <i>without your equation.</i>

52:52.002 --> 52:54.004
 <i>Uh, you interpreted it.</i>

52:54.379 --> 52:56.506
 <i>I interpreted your father.</i>

52:58.091 --> 52:59.968
 <i>Tell me about him.</i>

53:06.057 --> 53:07.559
 <i>Everything.</i>

53:15.859 --> 53:17.027
 <i>Um...</i>

53:18.111 --> 53:22.991
 <i>He was born on</i>
 <i>New Providence Island in, uh,</i>

53:24.201 --> 53:25.911
 <i>1955.</i>

53:28.413 --> 53:31.208
 <i>He made my dates come in</i>
 <i>and listen to Mingus.</i>

53:32.417 --> 53:34.544
 <i>It was mortifying.</i>

53:36.755 --> 53:38.215
 <i>But he is, uh...</i>

53:41.801 --> 53:45.764
 <i>I'm... I am so thankful.</i>

53:53.146 --> 53:57.943
 <i>So, God. Prayer.</i>

53:59.236 --> 54:03.198
 <i>The Anthean god</i>
 <i>is progress, efficiency.</i>

54:03.240 --> 54:05.533
 <i>That's what we worship.</i>

54:06.243 --> 54:08.536
 <i>Have we ever stopped to ask...</i>

54:09.788 --> 54:11.456
 <i>to what end?</i>

54:11.790 --> 54:13.416
<i>Humans do.</i>

54:13.458 --> 54:16.836
<i>They ask that in every moment.</i>

54:16.878 --> 54:18.964
<i>Every interaction.</i>

54:18.964 --> 54:20.966
<i>Every sunrise.</i>

54:20.966 --> 54:24.552
 <i>Because their God is meaning.</i>

54:25.303 --> 54:28.598
<i>Dinner together, meaning.</i>

54:31.142 --> 54:34.646
<i>A father's touch, meaning.</i>

54:35.522 --> 54:39.484
<i>A mother's strength, meaning.</i>

54:41.194 --> 54:45.115
 <i>At the beginning</i>
 <i>of this transmission, I asked,</i>

54:45.115 --> 54:49.286
 <i>"How is humanity</i>
 <i>beneficial to anything?</i>

54:50.578 --> 54:53.790
 <i>"Where does it fit</i>
 <i>in the universe?"</i>

54:55.292 --> 54:56.835
<i>Now I know.</i>

54:58.503 --> 55:00.839
<i>Find meaning in the moment</i>

55:01.589 --> 55:05.593
 <i>and the moment</i>
 <i>can become eternal.</i>

55:06.386 --> 55:09.139
 <i>Humanity is quantum.</i>

55:10.223 --> 55:13.768
 <i>Humanity is jazz.</i>

55:15.186 --> 55:16.771
 <i>And, wife...</i>

55:18.189 --> 55:19.983
 <i>it is beautiful.</i>
